Dear Players,

This version brings gameplay improvements, optimizations, and fresh new features;

MY STORY BOOK CLUB
• Connect with your friends and check out what they are reading
• Get diamond rewards
• Complete achievements
• Review stories

NEWSFEED:
• Stay updated at all times - newsfeed will notify you of your friends’ reading progress!

COMING SOON:
• Stay tuned for new and exciting stories and chapters of your favorite stories! We’re releasing new chapters every Tuesday!

Enjoy the game, and thank you for playing!
